title: I LOVE LISTS
description: I LOVE LISTS  How to help victims of the LA fires.  I would like to try a strawberry cloud. World sports photography awards. Amaze! These photos prove that our world is incredible.  Examples of good design. Why do we say up the wazoo? Is a shallot an onion? Have you tried this from Trader Joe’s? Let’s make savory dutch babies this year.  What happens when a natural disaster happens while on vacation? Let’s learn about Girl Scout Cookies. What shouldn’t you cook in a cast iron pan? Garden trends to look for in 2025. Food trends predicted for 2025. The complete history of music video. What to bring to the gym. Public domain image archive! What a fun discovery. How to work your way out of a food rut.  I am going to try to make a gf version of these biscuits. Weekend reading: The Let Them Theory     Need some help processing 2024 and prepping for 2025? Check out the workshops I’m cohosting with MC!  Intention Setting Online Workshop 2025 Saturday, January 11 10 AM-12 PM LIVE  $55 Includes printables!  The post I LOVE LISTS appeared first on Shutterbean.
excerpt: Welcome to I LOVE LISTS. It's Friday and Tracy of Shutterbean.com shares her finds from the internet on a weekly list called I LOVE LISTS!
